# 🍬 Bubblegum

Bubblegum is an AI software creation platform combining:

- Claude-style reasoning
- Lovable-style app generation
- Autonomous coding agents

## Features

✅ AI app planning  
✅ Code generation  
✅ Project architecture  
✅ AI developer assistant  
✅ Future autonomous deployment


## Vision

Bubblegum lets anyone describe an idea and receive a working application.